data.Name: Alan Parsons Live Project
data.Description: We are truly sorry to report that due to confirmed cases of Covid within members of our entourage, we are unable to continue with our current tour as scheduled. We sincerely regret the disappointment this will cause to our fans. My deepest apologies to anyone who has already made any travel arrangements for these two final shows. The last thing I would want to do is affect the health and wellbeing of any of you. More information will follow about rescheduling.
